markdownRemark.html: I get stressed out by the noise in my life. Social media, groupchats, keeping up with everything everyones talking about. I love my friends, but I am always trying to fit in - we all are really, and sometimes I like radio silence. Taking a break from it so I don’t forget that they are actually the most important people, along with my family, in my life and that the aspirations for what I want to be are second to who I want to be although you can’t really work your way to being a good person as clearly as you can working towards a goal.
